Here's some notes when writing RST for our final submission:

Title Hierarchy:

1) double ==================
2) -------------------------
3) ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
4) Single ==================
5) +++++++++++++++++++++++++

Italics: *word*
Bold: **word**

Mono-spaced text: ``some words``

Images:
http://docutils.sourceforge.net/docs/ref/rst/directives.html#images
